{"tid":989461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買「冰毒」收到冰糖　男氣到報警被拘留","createTime":"2019-01-21T01:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T10:58:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"391bf8b16aaae3d18d5900b2b48d3072b65d8d9e","tid":989461,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_d4dd17590efa3efa4ddf42eea68735a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_d4dd17590efa3efa4ddf42eea68735a3.jpg&h=636766ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王男到派出所報警，警方證實他買的「冰毒」是冰糖。翻攝《現代快報》<br />\n中國假貨橫行，連毒品都有假貨。江蘇省連雲港市一名王姓男子，近日花1,400元（約6,375元台幣），從一名毒販手上買來冰毒，不料他準備吸食時，發現「冰毒」竟然是冰糖！而他為追回金錢，還到派出所報警。警方向他問話時，他坦承日前曾吸毒，最後被拘留。<br />\n <br />\n王男到派出所報案時稱，他於上周二（15日）向一名姓周的毒販購買一批重1.59克的冰毒，到手後，他找了一個隱蔽的地方準備吸食，沒想到這批白色物體竟是冰糖，讓他十分氣憤。<br />\n <br />\n警方檢驗王男手上的所謂冰毒，確定是冰糖，不含毒品成份。但在問話期間，王男自爆在買毒品前幾日曾經吸毒，於是被警方拘留。警方已透過王男提供的線索，將周姓毒販拘捕。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190121/1504332/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190121%2F1504332%2F&d=7FZwGubSg%2Boc5%2FIyI3je97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=70e8bd50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190121%2F1504332%2F&h=e32ee28f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190121/1504332/</a>"},{"pid":"edd122b0ad1e865c7f67a68a828bd177453c04a3","tid":989461,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"有勇氣去自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c56c3be1ae040814d8ba358eafbe8b790fa4e4f","tid":989461,"uid":103230,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:29:15.000Z","msg":"佢冇俾包冰你咪算有良心<img src=